comments: Bey (DET) establishes position in front of Banchero (ORL) and legally boxes out the offensive player during the rebounding opportunity.
Banchero (ORL) momentarily places and removes a resting hand from Bogdanovic's (DET) body as the players move towards the ballhandler.
Banchero (ORL) moves along Ivey's (DET) path as marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Carter Jr. (ORL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Hampton (ORL) lowers his arm down and makes contact with the ball to disrupt Ivey's (DET) live dribble. Any arm contact after the dislodge is considered incidental.
Bogdanovic (DET) swipes at the ball and his arm passes in front of Banchero (ORL) without making any contact during the latter's layup attempt.
Banchero (ORL) briefly places his left arm on Bogdanovic's (DET) body and removes it as the offensive player proceeds towards a screening position. The contact in the play is marginal.
Banchero (ORL) legally contests Bogdanovic's (DET) perimeter shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (ORL) reaches his arms out to secure the rebound and his left arm makes contact with Stewart's (DET) right arm prior to any contact with the ball.
Stewart (DET) legally contests Wagner's (ORL) driving shot attempt.
Wagner (ORL) and Cunningham (DET) engage during the inbounds and the latter's arms come out as he releases away from the defender. The contact on the play is marginal.
Banchero (ORL) absorbs the contact from Cunningham (DET) as the former retreats during the driving shot attempt.
Ross (ORL) places and removes his hands from Stewart's (DET) body as Stewart launches into the air for the ball. The contact during the loose ball is marginal.
Bogdanovic (DET) collapses his left forearm as he jumps to defend Banchero's (ORL) driving shot attempt and the contact is marginal.
Banchero (ORL) moves alongside Cunningham's (DET) path after the pick, and the contact on the play is marginal.
Bogdanovic (DET) and Wagner (ORL) briefly engage and separate as they both retreat from the pick.
Wagner (ORL) steps to his right as Bogdanovic (DET) cuts into the lane and incidental foot-to-foot contact occurs as Cunningham releases his pass to the corner.
Stewart (DET) briefly places and then removes his arms from Banchero's (ORL) side during the inbounds play. The contact on the play is marginal.
Stewart (DET) legally contests the perimeter jump shot attempt from Ross (ORL).
Bey (DET) gets to ball height and cleanly dislodges the ball prior to incidental contact occurring with Banchero (ORL) on the follow through.
Ross (ORL) commits a take foul on Bogdanovic (DET). The transition take foul rule is not in effect with under two minutes to go in the fourth quarter.
Stewart's (DET) right hand makes contact with Wagner's (ORL) left arm during the offensive player's upward shooting motion.
